a.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old previously failed a gender eligibility test at the World Boxing Championships last year, with reports suggesting she had high levels of testosterone.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has been allowed to compete in Paris by the International Olympic Committee, despite the controversy surrounding her participation.And she's now hit back at critics in her first sit-down interview at the games.Imane Khelif has lashed out at critics at the Paris Olympics|REUTERSSpeaking to SNTV, she said the scrutiny over her gender was 'harmful to human dignity'.And she also suggested critics were bullying her, saying: \\\"I send a message to all the people of the world to uphold the Olympic principles and the Olympic Charter, to refrain from bullying all athletes, because this has effects, massive effects.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999667763865, \"rank\": 3.3223680178213804e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \